  <texture filename="helpImage5.png" width="128" height="128"/>

  <text name="introHelp" >
    <page>
      <p>[Xenowar]</p>
      <p>Xenowar. Copyright 2011 Lee Thomason / Grinning Lizard Software.</p>
      <p>
        Welcome to Xenowar! Xenowar is a turn based alien blasting strategy game. You can
        submit feedback, read the community forum, or get more gameplay information
        at xenowar.net.
      </p>
      <p> The buttons on the lower right navigate help, the lower left exits help.</p>
    </page>
    <page>
      <p>'New' starts a new game. The game auto-saves at exit and you can resume your current game with 'Continue'.</p>
      <p>If you choose a new game, you can select the skill level and number of your squad, the skill level and 
         number of aliens, and the terrain for the battle.
       </p>
      <p>Good luck and have fun!</p>
    </page>
  </text>


